73
00:02:47,364 --> 00:02:49,755
Thank you, I appreciated your support.

74
00:02:49,879 --> 00:02:50,391
Good.

75
00:02:50,495 --> 00:02:53,440
Now I hope you'll explain to me what's really going on.

76
00:02:53,686 --> 00:02:54,833
I thought I did.

77
