131
00:04:44,264 --> 00:04:46,864
Just unsecured nuclear materials.

132
00:04:50,359 --> 00:04:51,136
Yes.

133
00:04:51,216 --> 00:04:53,533
We're there, outside the evidence building.

134
00:04:54,158 --> 00:04:55,766
