167
00:06:38,942 --> 00:06:40,622
It was a misunderstanding,

168
00:06:40,784 --> 00:06:42,040
but it's past.

169
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:43,351
We are here.

170
00:06:43,669 --> 00:06:44,508
As an act of good faith,

171
00:06:44,672 --> 00:06:46,713
